{"about_the_game":"You are the leader of a Planetary Exploration Company, your goal is to explore planets to complete <strong>jobs </strong>and make your company <strong>survive</strong> and grow.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Combat</h2>A bullet heaven horde survival rogue-like. The combat is inspired in <i>Vampire Survivors</i>. Instead of collecting exp gems, you extract <strong>resources</strong> that your can use in different ways. Carefully plan your weapons and items inside a base to be ready to survive an exploration run. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797500/extras/screenshot-8-8-2022_-_small.png?t=1728248537\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Manage your company</h2>You have a <strong>huge bi-pedal robot</strong> to transport your <strong>employees </strong>you need to take care of. Use tens of <strong>items </strong>to <strong>upgrade </strong>them and avoid their destruction.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build items</h2>You can create tools and items for your employees and &quot;transport robot&quot;, research and unlock new technologies by extracting aliens resources and taking them to the<strong> research lab</strong>. Use them to change many aspects of the game.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797500/extras/items_long_1.png?t=1728248537\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endless game</h2>The game generates <strong>endless </strong>new planets you can visit and complete. Each planet has<strong> hundreds of map sectors</strong> to explore.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797500/extras/map_long_1.png?t=1728248537\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Invent your own weapons</h2>Research weapon components to<strong> mix and match </strong>different <strong>features </strong>to create your own player invented weapons.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797500/extras/weapon_inventor_1.png?t=1728248537\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story Events</h2>Encounter many story events told using weird <strong>symbols </strong>in an alien language, in them you have to decide which <strong>action </strong>to take, each decision can have powerful consequences.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797500/extras/story_1.png?t=1728248537\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Retro CRT effect</h2>Immerse yourself in the sci-fi experience with this optional post-processing effect. Here's a comparison of how it looks using it and not using it.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797500/extras/crt_comparison_small_1.png?t=1728248537\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797500/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728248537","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797500/page.bg.jpg?t=1728248537","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797500/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728248537","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797500/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728248537","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2173030,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"You are the leader of a Planetary Exploration Company, your goal is to explore planets to complete <strong>jobs </strong>and make your company <strong>survive</strong> and grow.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Combat</h2>A bullet heaven horde survival rogue-like. The combat is inspired in <i>Vampire Survivors</i>. Instead of collecting exp gems, you extract <strong>resources</strong> that your can use in different ways. Carefully plan your weapons